summaries.full: After reconsidering all the potential associates, Jenna narrows the pool to seven finalists and challenges them to find unique, locally crafted fashion, home, and beauty products for her pop-up shop. Meanwhile, Jenna and Sarah create a stunning photo booth for the celeb-studded SAG Awards, and Jenna puts the finishing touches on her false eyelash beauty line.

summaries.full: Pulling from a tricked-out mobile closet, Jenna and her team hit the road with four associates to help two women solve fashion dilemmas. After using new clothes and simple tricks to execute incredible style makeovers, the associates head back to NYC, where Jenna must decide whom to send packing.

summaries.short: A third group of associates sets out to create a fabulous table setting before two are chosen to help Jenna execute a fabulous party and photoshoot in LA.
summaries.full: Following another round of intense interviews, a third group of associates is tasked with designing a table setting for the company website’s upcoming LA dinner party/fashion shoot. Upon landing in LA, the pressure mounts as two associates work to execute a flawless, fabulous event at a stunning estate – all while attempting to meet Jenna’s exacting standards.
